Game information:

We're playing for the hero, who returns to the once
abandoned by people town and cleans it of all mischief.
In this world there is a war between the twin goddesses
Myrgato (Goddess of Darkness) and Alagath (Goddess of Light),
who managed to plunge the world into a river of blood and fear.
